==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''shack'''

#A small, crude [[cabin]]
#The grain left after harvest or gleaning; also, nuts which have fallen to the ground.
#Liberty of winter pasturage.
#A shiftless fellow; a low, itinerant beggar; a vagabond; a tramp.

